# Implementation Plan - Bug Fixes and UI Polish

This plan addresses several issues including missing system notifications, navigation enhancements, sorting capabilities, and UI alignment.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Sorting Button Relocation**: The plan replaces the section header collapse/expand button with the sorting button. This means sections will no longer be collapsible.
> **Notification Logic**: I will be integrating [WatchItem](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/WatchItem.kt#16-304) evaluation into the background [StockPriceUpdateWorker](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/StockPriceUpdateWorker.kt#20-142). This will increase the background work load slightly as it now evaluates all active watches.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Notifications Fix
Integrate [WatchItem](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/WatchItem.kt#16-304) alerts into the background update cycle.

#### [MODIFY] [StockPriceUpdateWorker.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/StockPriceUpdateWorker.kt)
- Fetch all active [WatchItem](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/WatchItem.kt#16-304)s from the database.
- Evaluate each [WatchItem](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/WatchItem.kt#16-304) using `AlertEvaluator.evaluate`.
- Check [canTrigger()](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/WatchItem.kt#230-255) for spam protection.
- Trigger system notifications for met conditions.
- Mark triggered watches as triggered in the database.

---

### 2. Swipe Navigation on Alerts
Allow users to swipe right on a watch item to go to the stock's detail page.

#### [MODIFY] [SwipeToDeleteCallback.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/ui/SwipeToDeleteCallback.kt)
- Update to support both `LEFT` (delete) and `RIGHT` (custom action) swipe directions.
- Add a callback for `onSwipedRight`.

#### [MODIFY] [AlertsFragment.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/AlertsFragment.kt)
- Configure `SwipeToDeleteCallback` to handle right swipes.
- On right swipe, call [navigateToStockDetailFromAlerts](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/MainActivity.kt#548-551) on [MainActivity](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/MainActivity.kt#57-2317).

---

