- Remove `CUSTOM` sort mode and associated logic.

#### [MODIFY] [GroupedWatchItemAdapter.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/GroupedWatchItemAdapter.kt)
- Remove expansion/collapse logic and `expandedSections`.
- Update [HeaderViewHolder](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/GroupedWatchItemAdapter.kt#277-349) to remove the expand icon and replace it with a sorting icon (or handle it in [MainActivity](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/MainActivity.kt#57-2317)).
- Remove `SortMode.CUSTOM` usage.

#### [MODIFY] [AlertAdapter.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/AlertAdapter.kt)
- Add sorting logic similar to [GroupedWatchItemAdapter](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/GroupedWatchItemAdapter.kt#53-441) but simplified for a flat list if necessary.

#### [MODIFY] [MainActivity.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/MainActivity.kt)
- Update the sorting menu in the toolbar for the Alerts tab.
- Remove "Anpassningsbar" (Custom) sorting option from menus.

