### 4. UI Polish
Fix alignment and colors.

#### [MODIFY] [fragment_alerts.xml](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/res/layout/fragment_alerts.xml) and [activity_main.xml](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/res/layout/activity_main.xml)
- Set `ProgressBar` visibility to `GONE` during pull-to-refresh to avoid double indicators.

#### [MODIFY] [MainActivity.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/MainActivity.kt)
- Change `FloatingActionButton` (plus button) background tint to `@color/pine_primary_dark` (the bright green used in switches).

#### [MODIFY] [Many files in ui/components/cards/](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/ui/components/cards/)
- Update [StockSummaryRow](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/ui/components/StockSummaryRow.kt#30-102), [PriceTargetCard](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/ui/components/cards/PriceTargetCard.kt#27-122), `MetricAlertCard`, `High52wCard`, `DailyMoveCard`, `CombinedAlertCard` to use `Alignment.Top` for right-aligned content.
- Ensure consistent top-padding and vertical alignment across all card types.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `AlertEvaluatorTest` to ensure evaluation logic is still sound.
- Create or update `StockPriceUpdateWorkerTest` to verify that notifications are triggered for [WatchItem](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/WatchItem.kt#16-304)s.

### Manual Verification
1. **Notifications**: Add a watch with a condition already met (or very close), ensure it triggers a system notification when background work runs (can be forced via ADB or by shortening interval).
2. **Swipe**: Go to "Bevakningar", swipe right on an item, verify it opens the correct stock detail page.
3. **Sorting**: Verify sorting works on both main lists and the Alerts page. Verify "Anpassningsbar" is gone.
4. **UI**: Check plus button color. Check card alignment (especially tickers vs prices). Verify no double indicators during refresh.
5. **Headers**: Verify headers are no longer collapsible and the icon is changed/removed as requested.
